h) Parking Requirements.
i)
Mixed use, multi-family and single-family lots shall provide 1.5 onsite parking
spaces/unit;
ii)
Commercial lots with an area less than 5000 ft2 have no requirements for onsite
parking; and,
iii)
Commercial lots with an area more than 5000 ft2 shall provide 1 onsite parking
space for every 600 ft2 of gross floor area.
